# Convert/Sheet — Excel & CSV to JSON Converter

A bespoke, high-fidelity developer utility to convert spreadsheet files (Excel and CSV) into clean JSON and vice-versa. Designed with a custom "Obsidian & Amber" theme, interactive spreadsheet data editing, multiple sheets support, and instant output copy/download actions.

Developed by [JoãoMRB](https://github.com/JoaoMRB).

## Features

- **Premium Responsive Interface** - Modern editorial layout built with a customizable Dark/Light mode theme.
- **Drag & Drop Canvas** - Elegant drop zone with active drag animations.
- **Interactive Data Grid** - Preview and edit spreadsheet cells directly with a double-click before generating JSON.
- **Multi-Sheet Support** - Read and convert multiple sheets simultaneously or choose a specific active sheet.
- **Advanced Export Controls** - Choose between flat or nested (dot-notation) JSON structures, array/object contentors, and minify or pretty-print settings.
- **Bi-Directional Conversion** - Generate JSON from Excel/CSV files, and convert valid JSON back into downloadable `.xlsx` spreadsheets.

## How to Run

1. Open the project folder.
2. Double-click [Index.html](./Index.html) or open it in any web browser.
3. Drag & drop or browse for an `.xlsx`, `.xls`, or `.csv` file to begin.

## Project Structure

- `Index.html` - Semantic markup and split-workspace layout structure.
- `styles.css` - Custom obsidian color tokens, switches, custom grid layout, and themes.
- `app.js` - Spreadsheet parsing logic, JSON builder, and DOM events.
